== generic operations
(call &infix:<->
(call &postcircumfix:<{ }>
(call &circumfix:<[ ]>
(call &prefix:<->
(call &postfix:<++>

== 'whatever' in various forms
[*-1]
@board[*;$_]
@prisoners.pick: *;
@lines.map(*».chars.max)
$x.polymod( 58 xx *)
… *
1..*
reduce * × 256 + *, $d, $c, $b, $a
Int $n where * > 0
(3 ** **)(^30)

